{"id":156704,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/黑客入侵pbs网站/","date":"2011-05-31T04:30:32Z","modified":"2011-05-31T04:30:32Z","title":"黑客入侵PBS网站","content":"<p>一组黑客上周六晚上入侵了美国公共广播公司（PBS）网站，在网站上贴了一篇虚构文章，声称说唱歌手吐派克·夏库尔还活着，目前生活在新西兰。除此之外，自称@LulzSec或The Lulz Boat的黑客组织还在pastebin.com上公布了PBS的MySQL数据库根密码，Frontline登录密码，以及用户密码和电子邮件地址。直到本周一，PBS仍然没有恢复对网站的控制，黑客仍然在恶意破坏网站。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://solidot.org.feedsportal.com/c/33236/f/556826/s/156bdc05/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<div>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tr>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/sendemail2.html?title=%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5PBS%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F30%2F0823258%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/emailthis2.gif\" /></a></td>\n<td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://res.feedsportal.com/viral/bookmark.cfm?title=%E9%BB%91%E5%AE%A2%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%B5PBS%E7%BD%91%E7%AB%99&#038;link=http%3A%2F%2Finternet.solidot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D11%2F05%2F30%2F0823258%26amp%3Bfrom%3Drss\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/images/bookmark.gif\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101095116470/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/156bdc05/a2.htm\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://da.feedsportal.com/r/101095116470/u/49/f/556826/c/33236/s/156bdc05/a2.img\" /></a></p>\n<div>\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=seyJa5q-Z_8:MSEZEyuocmk:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" /></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?a=seyJa5q-Z_8:MSEZEyuocmk:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/solidot?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" /></a>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://ww